SELECT `Reporting Month`, MAX(`Sales Amount-Order Retail445-30PrdMvAvg`) AS max_sales, MIN(`Reseller Order Quantity Long`) AS min_units
FROM `AdventureWorksDW2012Multidimensional-Handmade_main`.`ResellerPerspective`
GROUP BY `Reporting Month`
ORDER BY max_sales DESC, min_units
LIMIT 1

**Ratio of the previous two instructions:**
WITH 
  best_month_least_sales AS (
    SELECT `Reporting Month`, MIN(`Sales Amount-Order Retail445-30PrdMvAvg`) AS min_sales, MAX(`Reseller Order Quantity Long`) AS max_units
    FROM `AdventureWorksDW2012Multidimensional-Handmade_main`.`ResellerPerspective`
    GROUP BY `Reporting Month`
    ORDER BY min_sales, max_units DESC
    LIMIT 1
  ),
  best_month_greatest_sales AS (
    SELECT `Reporting Month`, MAX(`Sales Amount-Order Retail445-30PrdMvAvg`) AS max_sales, MIN(`Reseller Order Quantity Long`) AS min_units
    FROM `AdventureWorksDW2012Multidimensional-Handmade_main`.`ResellerPerspective`
    GROUP BY `Reporting Month`
    ORDER BY max_sales DESC, min_units
    LIMIT 1
  )
SELECT 
  (best_month_greatest_sales.max_sales / best_month_least_sales.min_sales) AS sales_ratio,
  (best_month_least_sales.max_units / best_month_greatest_sales.min_units) AS units_ratio
